{"tid":1036114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Carousell一物多賣老千呃30人十萬","createTime":"2019-02-25T04:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T04:12:13.000Z","uid":60517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5af3e94ea0339f1c2d53113d3d647bd081f932","tid":1036114,"uid":60517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"之前開po講過CHO小姐呢個大騙子<br />\n最後發現原來係蔡芷瑩個老千坐完監再出嚟呃錢！<br />\n<br />\n曹小姐 呃人最少廿十萬玩失蹤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ciObNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ciObNS</a><br />\n<br />\n名：CHO Hxx Lxx 6163 6696 (佢靠轉數快收錢）<br />\nCHOI TZE YING 90207779<br />\n<a href=\"http://whosnumber.com/hk/61636696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhosnumber.com%2Fhk%2F61636696&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Vtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=28b96578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://whosnumber.com/hk/61636696</a><br />\nSearch呢個電話號碼，原來已有多個人留言發聲<br />\n請大家留意呢個電話號碼，避免有人受騙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵人幫佢呃錢：<br />\n係Facebook同Carousell 賣Dyson 同二手Chanel, 聲稱無PayMe 搵其中一個買家幫佢代收再一次過用轉數快過返錢俾佢 (暫時有一個代收發現原來自己幫人呃錢，已經有最少55個受害人，金額達到最少二十萬港元）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/25/120537_01c4c030f35a2ad29232415d953a09f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2F120537_01c4c030f35a2ad29232415d953a09f2.png&h=415c8acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中有人提供佢資料，啱啱佢以買家身份買嘢，到sf 攞件<br />\n佢真名同電話可能係 Maple 68038124<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDAHUKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDAHUKV.png&h=6f5a25dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMynameisbitch絲打提供<br />\n&bull;<br />\n大家小心 以下係我有既資料<br />\n騙子電話: 51863054 (最常同我聯絡既電話) <br />\n96405299 (聲稱是她媽媽的電話)<br />\n90207779 (係佢轉數快既電話)（每次都通）<br />\n95249945 （曾用此電話聯絡我）<br />\n<br />\n佢有2個入數户口<br />\n第一個係經轉數快 電話係96405299 Choi T*** <br />\n第二個係户口 357 865534 882 Hui.F.S<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kD6geK6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkD6geK6.png&h=3ca2eb74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URzp747.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURzp747.png&h=a4f8f291&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUTN5RO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUTN5RO.png&h=1c7d27b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXDVviu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXDVviu.png&h=8de7b40d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQO2ULa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQO2ULa.png&h=231a03ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果報道：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190225/20620076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190225%2F20620076&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Vtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=e8b02a7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190225%2F20620076&h=270d1e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190225/20620076</a>"},{"pid":"716f829d4455d5a9204d197629b1917f5d73152b","tid":1036114,"uid":4231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"真條橋唔怕舊最緊要受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}